002300*    THE SUBPROGRAM IC117 DOES NOT CONTAIN A LINKAGE SECTION OR   IC1174.2
002400*    AN USING PHRASE IN THE PROCEDURE DIVISION HEADER.  DISPLAY   IC1174.2
