002000****************************************************************  IC2024.2
002100*        THE SUBPROGRAM IC202 IS CALLED BY THE PROGRAM IC201.  *  IC2024.2
002200*    THE SUBPROGRAM HAS FOUR OPERANDS IN THE USING PHRASE      *  IC2024.2
