054600     MOVE 1 TO CORRECT-18V0.                                      IC2034.2
054700     MOVE DN1 TO COMPUTED-18V0.                                   IC2034.2
054800     MOVE "DN1 INCORRECT" TO RE-MARK.                             IC2034.2
