002300 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.                                            IC2094.2
002400 CONFIGURATION SECTION.                                           IC2094.2
002500 SOURCE-COMPUTER.                                                 IC2094.2
002600     GNU-Linux.                                                   IC2094.2
