003100 01  DN1.                                                         IC2174.2
003200     02  DN2                     PICTURE X(5).                    IC2174.2
003300     02  DN3                     REDEFINES DN2   PICTURE 9(5).    IC2174.2
003400 01  DN4.                                                         IC2174.2
