063400     MOVE   "X" TO EXCEPTION-PATH-FLAG.                           IC2224.2
063500     MOVE   "X-28 5.2.4 (3)A" TO ANSI-REFERENCE.                  IC2224.2
063600     MOVE    ZERO TO DN3, DN4.                                    IC2224.2
