071700     MOVE    0 TO CALL-FLAG.                                      IC2224.2
071800     MOVE   "X" TO EXCEPTION-PATH-FLAG.                           IC2224.2
071900     MOVE   "X-28 5.2.4 (3)A" TO ANSI-REFERENCE.                  IC2224.2
