074000                   TO RE-MARK                                     IC2224.2
074100             MOVE "P" TO CORRECT-A                                IC2224.2
074200             MOVE EXCEPTION-PATH-FLAG TO COMPUTED-A               IC2224.2
074300             PERFORM FAIL                                         IC2224.2
074400     ELSE                                                         IC2224.2
