084500     ELSE                                                         IC2224.2
084600             MOVE   "INCORRECT CONTROL FLOW" TO RE-MARK           IC2224.2
084700             MOVE    1 TO CORRECT-N                               IC2224.2
084800             MOVE    CALL-FLAG TO COMPUTED-N                      IC2224.2
