043900*    STATEMENT.  THIS IS A SYNTACTICAL CHECK ONLY, THE ON         IC2244.2
044000*    OVERFLOW CONDITION SHOULD NEVER OCCUR.                       IC2244.2
044100     MOVE "ON OVERFLOW PHRASE" TO FEATURE.                        IC2244.2
