041900     MOVE   "PQRSTU"              TO WRK-DATA-2                   IC2274.2
042000     MOVE    123456               TO WRK-DATA-3                   IC2274.2
042100     MOVE    9876                 TO WRK-DATA-4.                  IC2274.2
