043800                             EXTERNAL-RECORD-WORK                 IC2274.2
043900                             F-S-PARAM.                           IC2274.2
044000     IF EXTERNAL-FILE-RECORD EQUAL EXTERNAL-RECORD-HOLD           IC2274.2
044100         PERFORM PASS                                             IC2274.2
044200     ELSE                                                         IC2274.2
