112100*                                                                 IC2274.2
112200*                                                                 IC2274.2
112300 PROCEDURE DIVISION USING ACTION-CODE                             IC2274.2
112400                          LINKAGE-RECORD-WORK                     IC2274.2
112500                          LINKAGE-FS.                             IC2274.2
112600*                                                                 IC2274.2
112700 SECT-IC227A-1-01 SECTION.                                        IC2274.2
