023100     IF P-OR-F EQUAL TO "FAIL*"  PERFORM WRITE-LINE               IC2284.2
023200        PERFORM FAIL-ROUTINE THRU FAIL-ROUTINE-EX                 IC2284.2
023300          ELSE PERFORM BAIL-OUT THRU BAIL-OUT-EX.                 IC2284.2
