027400      IF   INSPECT-COUNTER EQUAL TO ZERO                          IC2284.2
027500          MOVE "NO " TO ERROR-TOTAL                               IC2284.2
027600      ELSE MOVE INSPECT-COUNTER TO ERROR-TOTAL.                   IC2284.2
